  "detailed_description": "Create and Play bullet hell!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Very highly customizable bullet hell level editor.<br></li><li>Snap levels to a music to make it more interesting.<br></li><li>Load youtube video to stream music for the level.<br></li><li>Share levels using workshop in game.<br></li><li>Practice mode to play level from a specific point.<br></li><li>Replay mode to view your play.<br></li><li>Uses multithreading to calculate bullets.</li></ul><br>and some experimental features..<br><br>Editor Feature<br><br><br>Creating Patterns<br><br><br><strong>Create what you want</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/extras/e7360924dbc9d4160abfefee2bfa3fdf.avif?t=1594614870\" width=488 height=352 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/extras/40a627bb4a73ca5cd049640e449cf6e2.poster.avif?t=1594614870\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/extras/40a627bb4a73ca5cd049640e449cf6e2.webm?t=1594614870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/extras/40a627bb4a73ca5cd049640e449cf6e2.mp4?t=1594614870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/extras/07db9d025e613b3ed693b17d9b24937d.poster.avif?t=1594614870\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/extras/07db9d025e613b3ed693b17d9b24937d.webm?t=1594614870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269770/e